00:56:20.860 --> 00:56:21.850 align:middle line:90%
He was a real phony.

00:56:21.850 --> 00:56:22.990 align:middle line:90%
He had ideals.

00:56:22.990 --> 00:56:24.030 align:middle line:90%
He stood for something.

00:56:24.030 --> 00:56:24.830 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

